    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. The engine struggles to turn over and, once running, exhibits a rough idle and inconsistent power delivery, suggesting internal mechanical issues. Visually, the car shows significant wear, including noticeable body rust, fading paint, and a well-worn interior with several tears in the upholstery. While the car is mostly complete, it will require a substantial investment of time and money to return it to a reliable state.",
