    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips occasionally, while the exterior shows heavy rust and several large dents. Inside, the upholstery is torn and the electronics are largely non-functional, making this an ideal project car or source for parts for someone willing to put in the effort.",
