      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person. It's honestly in pristine condition\u2014I've babied it since day one and it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch on the paint and the interior is still spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. You really won't find one better than this!",
