    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 993 Carrera is a superlative example of air-cooled engineering, featuring the M64/21 3.6L flat-six equipped with the VarioRam resonance intake system for optimized volumetric efficiency. The G50/20 six-speed manual transaxle provides surgical shift precision, while the multi-link LSA rear axle maintains perfect kinematic toe-in under load. This chassis is free of any structural oxidation, and the top-end remains tight with zero oil migration at the valve covers or rear main seal. Recent leak-down testing shows less than 3% variance across all cylinders. Every bushing, synchro, and vacuum line functions at factory-spec tolerances. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade machine.",
      "price": 43500.0,
