      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster, free from any rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and has been treated with a high-end ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without any bolster wear or creasing, and the original floor mats are pristine. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in peak form, supported by a comprehensive, single-owner service history performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. It recently underwent a thorough preventative maintenance service, including a full fluid flush and multi-point inspection. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
